{"type":"message","id":"bab93452","parentId":"ad65583f","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:52:21.861Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-04-12 20:51 GMT+1] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: summarize this text:\n\nArtificial intelligence (AI) is rapidly transforming the way people live and work. From personalized recommendations on streaming platforms to advanced medical diagnostics, AI systems are becoming deeply embedded in everyday life. Businesses are increasingly adopting AI to automate routine tasks, improve decision-making, and enhance customer experiences. However, the growth of AI also raises important ethical concerns, such as data privacy, algorithmic bias, and job displacement. As governments and organizations work to establish regulations and best practices, the challenge lies in balancing innovation with responsibility. Ultimately, the future of AI will depend not only on technological advancements but also on how society chooses to guide its development."}],"timestamp":1776023541799}}
{"type":"message","id":"30c270ea","parentId":"bab93452","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:52:25.660Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Artificial intelligence (AI) is revolutionizing daily life and work by powering tools like personalized recommendations and medical diagnostics. Businesses leverage AI to enhance efficiency, decision-making, and user experiences. However, its rise brings ethical issues such as privacy risks, bias, and job loss. Striking a balance between fostering innovation and ensuring responsible use is critical. The future of AI hinges on both its technological progress and society’s ability to guide its growth responsibly."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"github-copilot","model":"gpt-4o","usage":{"input":10334,"output":90,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10424,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776023541850,"responseId":"chatcmpl-DTv8yVj8qzv11ZqB8LCoc8iwzHfYx"}}
